https://chatgpt.com/share/6926b71f-4cb4-8004-9319-91c00fad2cf3




✅ 4. Try mounting again
sudo mount -t nfs master:/cluster /cluster


or explicitly specify version (sometimes needed):

sudo mount -t nfs -o vers=4 master:/cluster /cluster


Or for NFSv3 (older servers):

sudo mount -t nfs -o vers=3 master:/cluster /cluster

✅ 5. Check if the NFS server is exporting properly (run this on master)
sudo exportfs -v


You should see something like:

/cluster  192.168.1.0/24(rw,sync,no_root_squash)


If not → the export isn’t set.

✅ 6. Test communication from worker2
showmount -e master


Expected:

Export list for master:
/cluster  192.168.1.0/24























Running:

sudo -iu mpi mpirun -np 6 \
  --hostfile /home/mpi/hostfile \
  --mca btl_tcp_if_exclude lo,docker0 \
  /cluster/matmul
